#: .\templates\about.html:101
msgid "Real Success Stories"
msgstr ""

#: .\templates\about.html:103
msgid "What Our Clients Say"
msgstr ""

#: .\templates\about.html:106
msgid ""
"Read reviews from businesses that trust our technical team for their "
"operational continuity."
msgstr ""

#: .\templates\about.html:123
msgid ""
"\"The restaurant AC failed on a Friday night in the middle of a summer "
"heatwave. With a full house, we called for their 24/7 emergency support. The "
"technician arrived in under an hour, diagnosed the compressor failure, and "
"repaired it that same night, saving our weekend sales. Prompt, impeccable "
"service with an honest price.\""
msgstr ""

#: .\templates\about.html:139
msgid ""
"\"We had recurring issues with the temperature of our cold storage rooms, "
"risking valuable food supplies. Nova Solutions conducted a deep audit, "
"detected micro-leaks that other technicians had ignored, and redesigned our "
"preventive maintenance plan. We haven’t lost any inventory since. Extremely "
"professional.\""
msgstr ""

#: .\templates\about.html:155
msgid ""
"\"Highly recommended for heavy industrial setups. We needed to optimize the "
"energy efficiency of the chillers at our plant to reduce high electricity "
"costs. Nova Solutions presented a clear project with no hidden fees and "
"worked cleanly, respecting our production hours. The energy savings were "
"immediate.\""
msgstr ""

#: .\templates\about.html:171
msgid ""
"\"Our commercial ice machine started acting up right before summer. The "
"technician not only fixed the mechanical issue in minutes but also performed "
"a deep sanitization of the water system. They explained the issue "
"transparently and gave us maintenance tips. Excellent and educational "
"service.\""
msgstr ""

